A question that
everyone asks when

00:03:05.420 --> 00:03:09.690 align:middle line:84%
they are exploring spirituality
is, what is my purpose?

00:03:09.690 --> 00:03:12.770 align:middle line:90%
What is my mission in life?

00:03:12.770 --> 00:03:18.660 align:middle line:84%
The idea, fundamentally, is
to learn to be your true self.

00:03:18.660 --> 00:03:20.600 align:middle line:90%
But what does that mean?

00:03:20.600 --> 00:03:24.650 align:middle line:84%
We all come in with the idea
of having chosen this life

00:03:24.650 --> 00:03:28.280 align:middle line:84%
with a theme or a
purpose or a challenge

00:03:28.280 --> 00:03:30.540 align:middle line:90%
to transform and overcome.

00:03:30.540 --> 00:03:33.080 align:middle line:84%
And the challenges that
we experience in life

00:03:33.080 --> 00:03:37.380 align:middle line:84%
are usually representative of
the themes that as a spirit,

00:03:37.380 --> 00:03:41.090 align:middle line:84%
we chose to explore
in physical reality.

00:03:41.090 --> 00:03:44.810 align:middle line:84%
But what does it mean to
really be your true self?

00:03:44.810 --> 00:03:50.600 align:middle line:84%
We all innately have a vibration
in our core, a frequency that is

00:03:50.600 --> 00:03:52.920 align:middle line:90%
our true essential frequency.

00:03:52.920 --> 00:03:56.670 align:middle line:84%
It is the frequency from
source, the frequency that

00:03:56.670 --> 00:04:00.820 align:middle line:84%
represents our connection to
existence and all that is.

00:04:00.820 --> 00:04:06.240 align:middle line:84%
It is the difference between the
frequency of our physical minds

00:04:06.240 --> 00:04:09.240 align:middle line:84%
and the frequency of
our core vibration

00:04:09.240 --> 00:04:13.410 align:middle line:84%
that we are attempting to
harmonize with in exploring

00:04:13.410 --> 00:04:16.350 align:middle line:90%
the idea of physical reality.

00:04:16.350 --> 00:04:19.660 align:middle line:84%
We are essentially
spirit beings.

00:04:19.660 --> 00:04:23.860 align:middle line:84%
According to Bashar, we never
really leave the spirit realm.

00:04:23.860 --> 00:04:27.270 align:middle line:84%
While in spirit, we have
taken a portion of ourselves,

00:04:27.270 --> 00:04:30.910 align:middle line:84%
and we have focused
it into this dream,

00:04:30.910 --> 00:04:33.420 align:middle line:84%
into this experience
or this illusion

00:04:33.420 --> 00:04:35.890 align:middle line:90%
that we call physical reality.

00:04:35.890 --> 00:04:40.630 align:middle line:84%
So from Bashar's perspective,
spirit is our natural state.

00:04:40.630 --> 00:04:42.190 align:middle line:90%
It's where we live.

00:04:42.190 --> 00:04:45.150 align:middle line:84%
But we have allowed a
portion of ourselves

00:04:45.150 --> 00:04:48.390 align:middle line:84%
to have this
experience by imposing

00:04:48.390 --> 00:04:51.900 align:middle line:84%
belief systems on
ourselves that create

00:04:51.900 --> 00:04:56.580 align:middle line:84%
a physical mind, a focused mind
that allows us to experience

00:04:56.580 --> 00:04:59.160 align:middle line:84%
physical reality as
if it is something

00:04:59.160 --> 00:05:01.690 align:middle line:90%
more solid than an illusion.

