basically limitless beings,

00:05:11.950 --> 00:05:13.300 align:middle line:90%
timeless beings.

00:05:13.300 --> 00:05:17.590 align:middle line:84%
We can know all the answers
to all the questions.

00:05:17.590 --> 00:05:21.000 align:middle line:84%
