something new, in order

00:05:21.000 --> 00:05:24.850 align:middle line:84%
to expand creation, we
have to, in a sense,

00:05:24.850 --> 00:05:28.080 align:middle line:84%
forget who we are so
that we can remember

00:05:28.080 --> 00:05:30.430 align:middle line:84%
who we are from a
new point of view,

00:05:30.430 --> 00:05:34.300 align:middle line:84%
discover something, a new
perspective of ourselves.

00:05:34.300 --> 00:05:37.320 align:middle line:84%
And that is how
creation expands.

00:05:37.320 --> 00:05:43.240 align:middle line:84%
