it, our experience of it,

00:05:47.050 --> 00:05:51.950 align:middle line:84%
our perspective of existence
that always changes.

00:05:51.950 --> 00:05:55.570 align:middle line:84%
And that is how creation
expands and experiences

00:05:55.570 --> 00:05:59.200 align:middle line:84%
expansion, through
us, of itself.

00:05:59.200 --> 00:06:02.650 align:middle line:84%
